    <item>
      <title>嘉能可切断煤炭生产以停止延长价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/glencore-to-cut-coal-production-to-halt-prolonged-price-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Glencore PLC表示，它正在切割计划的煤炭生产，这是世界上最肮脏的燃料中最大的托运人，希望停止价格长时间的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/glencore-to-cut-coal-production-to-halt-prolonged-price-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:11:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯，乌克兰认为停火并不令人满意，比继续战争更糟糕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/russia-ukraine-see-unsatisfactory-ceasefire-worse-than-continued-war-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国情报界的一项评估，俄罗斯和乌克兰可能会看到更大的动力延长三年冲突，而不是急于解决方案，该评估与唐纳德·特朗普总统的承诺迅速结束了为期三年的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/russia-ukraine-see-unsatisfactory-ceasefire-worse-than-continued-war-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
